ZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家經歷過這兩星期的抗爭運動都辛苦了! 雖然「五大訴求」(包括埋「林鄭下台」)仍然未達到，但希望大家趁呢兩日先好好地休息，之後重新裝備再齊齊繼續抗爭吧~<br />\n<br />\n不過，有啲事就真係比較急嘅，就係 - <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">距離今屆新選民登記嘅截止日期<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>仲剩番10日咋</strong></span>!!!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果你自己、兄弟姐妹、同事朋友等等仲未登記嘅，請好好把握今次嘅機會立即登記，以便喺<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins><span style=\"color: violet;\">今年24/11嘅區議會選舉</span></ins></span> 同 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"color: pink;\">出年立法會選舉</span></ins></strong></span>，將一個一個賣港又冇立場嘅親共政棍跟尾狗狠狠地踢出議會，將議會嘅否決權還番俾人民吧!!!<br />\n(可惜嘅係，已登記選民嘅更改資料期限已經喺2/6結束了，但大家仍需要覆查自己嘅選民資料有冇俾人更改／刪除咗，尤其係最近換咗新身分證嘅朋友)<br />\n<br />\n有關選民登記嘅資料如下：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">《地方選區選民》</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-1%28C&d=UYGl2U%2FUD6QdVJGaYMmpaFGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=1217bbb5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C</a>).pdf<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">《功能界別選民及／或選舉委員會界別分組選民》</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-41(C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-41%28C&d=UYGl2U%2FUD6QdVJGaYMmpaFGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=7381fca4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-41(C</a>).pdf<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">網上更新電郵地址</span></strong> - <a href=\"https://www.ospprdtwdc.reo.gov.hk/osp/ra008/mainEM.jsp&hellip;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ospprdtwdc.reo.gov.hk%2Fosp%2Fra008%2FmainEM.jsp%E2%80%A6&d=UYGl2U%2FUD6QdVJGaYMmpaFGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=db405458\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ospprdtwdc.reo.gov.hk/osp/ra008/mainEM.jsp&hellip;</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">選民資料網上查閱系統</span></span></strong> - <a href=\"https://www2.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/web/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.voterinfo.gov.hk%2Fbd_reovi%2FOVIES%2Fjsp%2Fweb%2F&d=UYGl2U%2FUD6QdVJGaYMmpaFGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=082b749f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/web/</a></span><br />\n<br />\n此外，資料組嘅朋友可以好好地利用呢段時間，儲齊呢段時間來班建制狗所做嘅「好人好事」並作出整理，成為「彈藥」以供文宣組嘅朋友製作長輩圖及其他文案等，對一眾被利用嘅中年／老人家作出「反洗腦」宣傳，辛苦大家了！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>＊＊＊ <span style=\"color: pink;\">齊心登記</span>，<span style=\"color: pink;\">一齊投票</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">用選票拆散保皇狗</span> ＊＊＊</strong></span>"},{"pid":"845242e609186692724e66d8b78014937ca1e4c4","tid":1252701,"uid":70403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T07:05:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">啲高官死撚梗！</span>"}]}